ges/1357458696/image_1357458696.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4745309-chiq-beneficiary-of-shifting-household-sentiment-policy-commitment-in-2025", "pub_date": "2024-12-19 16:35:08"}, {"id": "4745306", "title": "Rivian Is The EV Stock To Hold In 2025, Not Tesla (Upgrade)", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1288508380/image_1288508380.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Rivian headquarters in Silicon Valley\" data-id=\"1288508380\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"6696px\" height=\"4466px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1288508380/image_1288508380.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1288508380/image_1288508380.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1288508380/image_1288508380.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1288508380/image_1288508380.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1288508380/image_1288508380.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1288508380/image_1288508380.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1288508380/image_1288508380.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1288508380/image_1288508380.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">Sundry Photography</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>The story of Tesla (<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/TSLA\" title=\"Tesla, Inc.\">TSLA</a>) and Rivian (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NASDAQ:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/RIVN\" title=\"Rivian Automotive, Inc.\">RIVN</a></span>) in the stock market this year is a tale of two opposites: and an industry that has been surprisingly been supercharged by political affiliations as well. Tesla, the world's</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1288508380/image_1288508380.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4745306-rivian-is-the-ev-stock-to-hold-in-2025-not-tesla-upgrade", "pub_date": "2024-12-19 16:31:25"}, {"id": "4745301", "title": "PeptiDream: Opulent Dream Now A Reality", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture><img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1346182684/image_1346182684.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Smiling man sleeping in a bed covered with dollars\" data-id=\"1346182684\" data-type=\"getty-image\" fetchpriority=\"high\"></picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-credits\">tiero</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <h2>A New Year, a New Molecule Class</h2> <p>While the cell and gene therapy industry once held much promise and allowed investors to capitalize on the great new trend in biotechnology, high costs, and stubborn IP developments have hamstrung the industry over</p>", "image": null, "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4745301-peptidream-opulent-dream-now-a-reality", "pub_date": "2024-12-19 16:26:03"}, {"id": "4745321", "title": "Where Do Stocks Go From Here?", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1316474343/image_1316474343.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Multi exposure of abstract financial diagram on office buildings background, banking and accounting concept\" data-id=\"1316474343\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1024px\" srcset=\"htt