le/4719801-grupo-televisa-stock-mispricing-is-absurd\">wrote</a> about Grupo Televisa (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NYSE:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/TV\" title=\"Grupo Televisa, S.A.B.\">TV</a></span>) with the thesis that the stock was absurdly mispriced with growing cash flow and a 45% stake in TelevisaUnivision that was worth around $3-4 per share. Since</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1490711734/image_1490711734.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4745297-grupo-televisa-excellent-efficiency-improvements-improve-cash-flow", "pub_date": "2024-12-19 16:01:32"}, {"id": "4745175", "title": "CRBD: The First Exchange-Traded Debt Issue Of Corebridge Financial", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2021524839/image_2021524839.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Business finance and investment, Analyze economic growth charts for informed business finance decisions and financial decision-making. Stock Market report, Strategy, Data Collection, Forecasting\" data-id=\"2021524839\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"910px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2021524839/image_2021524839.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2021524839/image_2021524839.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2021524839/image_2021524839.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2021524839/image_2021524839.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2021524839/image_2021524839.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2021524839/image_2021524839.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2021